# **CV Master**

> An AI-powered CV evaluation platform for students and job seekers.

CV Master helps you **analyze, score, and improve your CV** using Google's Gemini API. It also provides **skill extraction**, **skill gap analysis**, and **grammar/style feedback**, helping you prepare for your dream role.

---

## **ğŸš€ Features**

* **CV Evaluation** â€“ AI-based assessment tailored to your chosen role.
* **Skill Extraction** â€“ Identify both technical and soft skills.
* **Skill Gap Analysis** â€“ Compare CV skills against job descriptions.
* **Scoring System** â€“ Rate your CV based on clarity, relevance, and skill match.
* **Grammar & Formatting Check** â€“ Suggestions for better readability and style.
* **Role-Based Customization** â€“ Choose from predefined roles or specify your own.

